Process Checklist — Pub/Sub Triggered Cloud Function
1.	Enable APIs (pubsub, cloudfunctions, cloudbuild, eventarc)
2.	Create Pub/Sub topic (gcloud pubsub topics create TOPIC)
3.	Write main.py (use @functions_framework.cloud_event) + requirements.txt
4.	Create runtime SA
5.	Deploy with --trigger-topic=TOPIC + --run-service-account=SA (fixes auth issues)
6.	Publish test message (gcloud pubsub topics publish TOPIC --message="...")
7.	Check logs (gcloud functions logs read FUNCTION --region=REGION --gen2)
